metrics.visualTitle: Top 10 des communes les plus énergivores

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Existant"}, 'BDD_Fusion'[Logements])

	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'BDD_Fusion'[Nom__commune_(BAN)],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumConsommation_Totale_kWh", CALCULATE(SUM('BDD_Fusion'[Consommation_Totale_kWh]))
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(10, __SQDS0Core, [SumConsommation_Totale_kWh], 0)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'BDD_Fusion'[Nom__commune_(BAN)],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__SQDS0BodyLimited,
			"SumConsommation_Totale_kWh", CALCULATE(SUM('BDD_Fusion'[Consommation_Totale_kWh]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [SumConsommation_Totale_kWh], 0, 'BDD_Fusion'[Nom__commune_(BAN)], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[SumConsommation_Totale_kWh] DESC, 'BDD_Fusion'[Nom__commune_(BAN)]

metrics.visualTitle: Évolution de la Consommation Totale (kWh) par Année de Construction
Moyenne de Consommation_Totale_kWh par Etiquette_DPE, lat et lon

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Existant"}, 'BDD_Fusion'[Logements])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'adresses-41'[lat],
			'adresses-41'[lon],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('BDD_Fusion'[Consommation_Totale_kWh]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'adresses-41'[lat]", 'adresses-41'[lat],
			"'adresses-41'[lon]", 'adresses-41'[lon],
			"'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh", [AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'adresses-41'[lat], 'adresses-41'[lon])

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'adresses-41'[lat]", 'adresses-41'[lat],
			"'adresses-41'[lon]", 'adresses-41'[lon],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 1,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'adresses-41'[lat],
			1,
			'adresses-41'[lon],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0Primary,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'adresses-41'[lat], 'adresses-41'[lon], [ColumnIndex]

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"D"}, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Neuf"}, 'BDD_Fusion'[Logements])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'adresses-41'[lat],
			'adresses-41'[lon],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('BDD_Fusion'[Consommation_Totale_kWh]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'adresses-41'[lat]", 'adresses-41'[lat],
			"'adresses-41'[lon]", 'adresses-41'[lon],
			"'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh", [AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'adresses-41'[lat], 'adresses-41'[lon])

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'adresses-41'[lat]", 'adresses-41'[lat],
			"'adresses-41'[lon]", 'adresses-41'[lon],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 1,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'adresses-41'[lat],
			1,
			'adresses-41'[lon],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0Primary,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'adresses-41'[lat], 'adresses-41'[lon], [ColumnIndex]

			"'adresses-41'[lon]", 'adresses-41'[lon],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [AverageConsommation_Totale_kWh]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 1,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'adresses-41'[lat],
			1,
			'adresses-41'[lon],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0Primary,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'BDD_Fusion'[Etiquette_DPE]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'adresses-41'[lat], 'adresses-41'[lon], [ColumnIndex]
